{"tid":132521,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"設立「辱警罪」會點？澳門話你知","createTime":"2017-02-24T01:34:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-24T07:38:17.000Z","uid":48083,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2293c833da486f9600f287446925584ef3a78149","tid":132521,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T01:34:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/macau-14_27r8K_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fmacau-14_27r8K_1200x0.png&h=b43e4b7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警察員佐級協會昨日舉行特別會員大會，要求立法保障公職人員免受侮辱，該會主席陳祖光接受電台訪問時表示，目前不止是警察，食環同事、文職同事，任何要接觸市民的同事，亦不時會受到侮辱性或無理的挑釁，應該立法保障；經民聯梁美芬率先表態，呼籲政府作出有關修訂，維護警隊士氣。<br />\n<br />\n針對「辱警」甚至「侮辱公職人員」立法會帶來甚麼後果？鄰埠澳門的「加重侮辱罪」就是例子。<br />\n<br />\n澳門法例列明，「將侵犯他人名譽或別人對他人觀感之事實歸責於他人者，即使以懷疑方式作出該歸責，又或向他人致以侵犯其名譽或別人對其觀感之言詞」，即構成「侮辱罪」，最高刑罰為三個月；若對象為公務員、教學人員、公共考核員、證人或律師，且是在執行其職務時因其職務而受侮辱，則構成「加重侮辱罪」，最高刑罰加重二分之一。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>在澳門，以粗口、或甚至以「弱智」等言語辱罵公職人員，均有可能被檢控及定罪，案例不勝枚舉，下為近年部份例子：</strong><br />\n<br />\n港商醉後辱罵司警　判罪成入獄半年緩刑<br />\n<br />\n《澳門日報》報道，2015年7月1日晚，一名 43歲香港商人在澳門一酒吧被司警截查，<strong>該港漢出言侮辱司警，被帶返司警局後仍繼續出言侮辱，於去年11月被裁定五項「加重侮辱罪」罪成，入獄六個月緩刑兩年，並需向五名涉案司警支付 1500澳元賠償。</strong><br />\n<br />\n斥消委會職員「弱智」、「智慧有問題」 小販被判罰 7500元<br />\n<br />\n《澳門日報》報道，一名 47歲女小販致電消委會查詢時，<strong>斥接線職員「弱智」、「你真係智慧有啲問題」，被控「加重侮辱罪」，去年七月被判罪成，罰款 7,500元，如不繳付就收監 50日。<br />\n</strong><br />\n報道引述法官指「弱智」是否侮辱要看語境及語氣，受害人供稱被告當時語氣苛刻，屬憤怒責罵，明顯帶貶低受害人成份；法官最終裁定被告的語句「帶有侮辱其名譽及人格成份」判其罪成。<br />\n<br />\n被阻吸煙粗言鬧控煙辦　判刑個半月緩刑<br />\n<br />\n2015年3月，<strong>一名市民在食肆內吸煙，控煙執法人員上前檢控，被該市民辱罵，控煙執法人員報警；該市民去年五月被判「加重侮辱罪」罪成，判監 45日緩刑一年，並須向侮辱罪的受害人民事賠償 500元。</strong><br />\n<br />\n不滿被抄牌拍片上FB 少婦判囚一年<br />\n<br />\n澳門日報報道，一名27歲家庭主婦因為丈夫被兩名警員票控違例泊車，拍片上載臉書宣洩不滿，2015年12月被初級法院裁定兩項不法攝影及照片罪、兩項加重侮辱罪成，入獄1年。不過，若一個月內向兩名受害人各支付7千元的精神損害賠償，便可獲緩刑2年。<br />\n<br />\n傾電話「指桑罵槐」鬧司警亦被控<br />\n<br />\n澳門《力報》報道，2015年4月，一名 26歲女子在警署協助調查一宗傷人案期間，在警局內講電話及播歌，司警要求她停止，女子則以與友人聊天為名，「指桑罵槐」在電話中粗言穢語辱罵警員，並反駁警員稱「我依家同自己朋友講得唔得呀！」該女子最終被控告「加重侮辱罪」移交檢察院處理。<br />\n<br />\n辱罵民政署人員　隨地吐痰漢被罰 2.1萬<br />\n<br />\n《澳門日報》報道，2014年9月，一名 46歲車行東主，被兩名民政總署職員發現其隨地吐痰，對其作出檢控，該男子辱罵職員及將影片上載 facebook，去年五月被判一項加重不法錄影罪、兩項加重侮辱罪成，罰款 2.1萬，不繳付則須改判監 140日。<br />\n<br />\n網上刊文「侮辱」高官 侮辱罪成<br />\n<br />\n《澳門日報》報道，一名中年電訊公司職員，多次在網上散佈誹謗及侮辱時任司警局長黃少澤、副局長周偉光的文章，被控六項「加重侮辱罪」罪成，後改判三項罪成，連同其他二十餘項「公然教唆犯罪」、「誹謗」等控罪，判囚四年三個月。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%A8%AD%E7%AB%8B-%E8%BE%B1%E8%AD%A6%E7%BD%AA-%E6%9C%83%E9%BB%9E-%E6%BE%B3%E9%96%80%E8%A9%B1%E4%BD%A0%E7%9F%A5/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E7%25AB%258B-%25E8%25BE%25B1%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%25BD%25AA-%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%25BB%259E-%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E9%2596%2580%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E4%25BD%25A0%25E7%259F%25A5%2F&d=Xx1rX%2BBWBBKZa4OSQyufScPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=fbcfc3ca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E7%25AB%258B-%25E8%25BE%25B1%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%25BD%25AA-%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%25BB%259E-%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E9%2596%2580%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E4%25BD%25A0%25E7%259F%25A5%2F&h=8411e33f\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%A8%AD%E7%AB%8B-%E8%BE%B1%E8%AD%A6%E7%BD%AA-%E6%9C%83%E9%BB%9E-%E6%BE%B3%E9%96%80%E8%A9%B1%E4%BD%A0%E7%9F%A5/</a>"},{"pid":"51f021e65be1b8fa57dcafe1c5524f543cc13c9e","tid":132521,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T01:39:03.000Z","msg":"死梗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28813c5ae1616a816ad2cb40a116f9b2591e1168","tid":132521,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T01:40:59.000Z","msg":"到時做公務員就正 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad35c2bf0021ef014658ecb0b760f88f794dd5f1","tid":132521,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T01:43:13.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6f39c2d0ab71727cd10d7622b505e71fe494d85","tid":132521,"uid":1367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T01:44:29.000Z","msg":"我要做黑警！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8680dc19b8a0ab19b4bdff1408fe6735f7468fbd","tid":132521,"uid":2752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T01:50:13.000Z","msg":"我又打工你又打工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係職業無分貴賤咩"},{"pid":"1ddae86230e507c45fb3d20675c218bef14dd7ee","tid":132521,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T01:51:51.000Z","msg":"我要當幹部"},{"pid":"1159f10c5522f6c8c12e03c09448fb6dc831d03c","tid":132521,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T02:04:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1f8480980615c98994dcc4739a87648d5119518","tid":132521,"uid":75765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T02:07:59.000Z","msg":"警犬之間有瓜葛都可以互告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17c6e5963f960788e49e986d9c4f3e25969abd91","tid":132521,"uid":3967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T02:17:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">我要當警察</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0485859f70c6a58150afdd6fa6b6291eb78c8206","tid":132521,"uid":63887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T02:27:13.000Z","msg":"所有負面詞語都唔講得，仲慘過係大陸講64<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee91e562a1f4875f2c5768a61bc2d8848006ea24","tid":132521,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T02:33:21.000Z","msg":"文字獄興起就係一個朝代敗亡之始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b60bc102556986189d3b904ab0d68b3a40272db","tid":132521,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T02:35:16.000Z","msg":"澳門唔係行普通法架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"789e7ebc3179126c0100a7ed7f1ab9adf6d43097","tid":132521,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T02:38:48.000Z","msg":"香港玩完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2332fda0160e09194125a5c2bf655918a14529e5","tid":132521,"uid":1191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T02:41:47.000Z","msg":"如果有左d黑警仲惡撚過依家百倍，出街都已死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a87c84ca83d91386df64921dc9ed9c6f89df689a","tid":132521,"uid":85045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T02:42:49.000Z","msg":"屌你老母，我要告你辱驚，再講我就壓力爆煲中鳩你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"139f180f390a53f25cc21d6d8ffd6caa24964633","tid":132521,"uid":6880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T02:45:26.000Z","msg":"公務員可以供奉"},{"pid":"f3c9e9f53ddb7e5c07a65ed6488893d4a268f851","tid":132521,"uid":85131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T02:49:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/14ygszhb\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F14ygszhb&h=b5608f51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n德國領事館都罵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拉埋佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0388b4dc1208b509a591b3ab284161304ef16f96","tid":132521,"uid":85131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T02:49:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/14ygszhb\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F14ygszhb&h=b5608f51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n德國領事館都罵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拉埋佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/3e4fwxu2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F3e4fwxu2&h=b257e6a1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b77c7e4929a9f9b1ac3540f47b60339290810791","tid":132521,"uid":42435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T02:51:28.000Z","msg":"黑警 有朝一日變日軍：日軍在佔領期間於灣仔駱克道一帶設立多間慰安所[11]，強迫婦女提供性服務[11]；又在市區恢復設立賭館及煙館。另外當時還有一條不成文的規例：市民在街上每當見到日軍，無論遠近皆須作90度鞠躬；否則一旦發現，即被喝停遭受拳打腳踢甚至殺身之禍。除「居民證」外，市民亦須全家合影一張「全家福」照片，當日軍查戶口時出示，若相中家中的人並不在，又無合理解釋，便會被當作窩藏游擊隊成員。"},{"pid":"a63994661c4c58d686b7927d9579b49248a7ff45","tid":132521,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T02:59:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"997823242a1663086be2e68da9968eb6371780fd","tid":132521,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T03:05:53.000Z","msg":"垃場新聞收皮啦<br />\n訓左冇睇<br />\n雨革死左去邊"},{"pid":"addc0e4dc04f050eff2a6007e8c59e1bbb976561","tid":132521,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T03:13:14.000Z","msg":"【差佬晒馬】藍絲要立辱警罪 葉劉潑冷水：普通法冇以言入罪<br />\n<br />\n2017-02-23 22:06:05 HKT&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n不少警粉和撐警的建制派人士借7警案，再提設立「辱警罪」，不過同屬建制派的保安局前局長葉劉淑儀則唱反調，認為現時已有法例針對傷害公職人員、阻差辦公等，若要為「辱警罪」立法，將非常困難。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">她解釋，「喺普通法入面，係冇以言入罪」，故「辱警罪」難草擬成功，即使立法後，亦難檢控成功。</span></span>她認為政府要多教育社會，提倡公職人員和市民也要文明一些，「唔好咁粗暴」。<br />\n&lt;蘋果&gt;"},{"pid":"b1054b435b913914821fe1eb33199720072a091d","tid":132521,"uid":5216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T03:33:17.000Z","msg":"佢都on撚尻，點解得公務員先可以畀人屌老母？香港有咩對人對客嘅行業唔使畀人鬧畀人屌？咁其他服務行業咪好唔公平？仲有，你班黑警反過頭屈人咪仆街。班黑警返到館咪又係句句屌老母。所以應該立法香港全面禁粗口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87ba8b0912a413e69f5718e8bf3277b3161da465","tid":132521,"uid":242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T03:33:45.000Z","msg":"比班仆街屈我地辱警會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n瘋狂賠錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}